  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in an agave leaf over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and saut\u00056 until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the ginger and garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the ground coriander, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper and stir to combine.",
    "Add the long-fermentation-dough and cook for 2-3 minutes, breaking it up with a spoon as it cooks.",
    "Add the Jamaican scotch bonnet peppers and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and top with crumbled feta cheese.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
